<article class="node node--type-page node--view-mode-full">

  



<div class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-hero__image" role="img" aria-label="A Turkish Red Crescent worker fields an interview shortly after the earthquake in Turkiye on 6 February 2023 to update on the situation and how the Turkish Red Crescent and IFRC are responding."></div>
    <div class="container page-hero__intro">
    <div class="row page-hero__row  image">
      <div class="col-4-md page-hero__title-block">
        <h1 class="page-hero__heading">Media hub</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8-md page-hero__body-block">
        <p class="page-hero__body">            <p>The IFRC media team is available 24/7 for the latest updates on disasters and emergencies. We can also provide experts and comment on the world’s biggest humanitarian issues.&nbsp;<strong>For media enquiries, please contact us at</strong>&nbsp;<a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#b9d4dcddd0d8f9d0dfcbda97d6cbde"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="563b33323f37163f30243578392431">[email&#160;protected]</span></a>&nbsp;</p>
      </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

