<article id="block-abouttheifrc">

  



<div class="footer-description">

  <h2 class="footer-description__heading">About the IFRC</h2>
  
  <div class="footer-description__body">
  

            <p>The IFRC is the world’s largest humanitarian network, comprising 191 National Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies working to save lives, build community resilience, strengthen localization and promote dignity around the world.</p>

      
</div>
